OL,3,CBody recovered off beach after
OL,4,C'concerns for man in water'
OL,6,FA man's body has been recovered off
OL,7,FBrighton beach.
OL,9,FSussex Police said emergency services
OL,10,Fattended the city's beachfront near to
OL,11,FSea Lanes in Madeira Drive at around
OL,12,F6.40am on Wednesday after concerns for
OL,13,Fa man in the water.
OL,15,FA force spokeswoman said: "The body of
OL,16,Fa man was recovered from the sea, and
OL,17,Fsadly, he was pronounced deceased at
OL,18,Fthe scene.
OL,20,F"Attempts to identify the man and
OL,21,Fnotify his next of kin remain ongoing.
