OL,3,CBody recovered off beach after
OL,4,C'concerns for man in water'
OL,6,F"Officers will continue carrying out
OL,7,Finquiries in the area, and an
OL,8,Fincreased police presence is expected
OL,9,Fat this time."
OL,11,FThe recovery of the man's body is the
OL,12,Flatest in a number of recent water-
OL,13,Frelated incidents in the Brighton area.
OL,15,FThe bodies of Jane Adetoro, 36,
OL,16,FChristina Walters, 32, and Rebecca
OL,17,FWalters, 31, were recovered from the
OL,18,Fsea near Black Rock car park in
OL,19,FMadeira Drive on May 13.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NO]
