OL,3,CBody recovered off beach after
OL,4,C'concerns for man in water'
OL,6,FEmergency services were called after
OL,7,Fconcerns were raised for a person's
OL,8,Fwelfare at around 5.45am.
OL,10,FAn inquest opening into the deaths of
OL,11,Fthe sisters, who lived together in
OL,12,FGreenford, west London, heard that
OL,13,F"medical investigations are ongoing to
OL,14,Ffinalise the cause of death" for all
OL,15,Fthree women, but at this stage police
OL,16,Fare satisfied there was no third party
OL,17,Finvolvement.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@\O]
