OL,3,CBody recovered off beach after
OL,4,C'concerns for man in water'
OL,6,FTheir father paid tribute to them as
OL,7,Fhis joy and strength, and "beautiful
OL,8,Flight that filled our family with
OL,9,Fhappiness and love".
OL,11,FIn a separate incident, on May 29,
OL,12,Fpolice were called to Rottingdean
OL,13,Fbeach, near Brighton, after a report
OL,14,Fof a man's body being found.
OL,16,FHe was identified as a 50-year-old man
OL,17,Ffrom Hertfordshire and the incident
OL,18,Fwas being treated "unexplained" at the
OL,19,Ftime, according to Sussex Police.
